<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA621_05_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema621_05.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema621_05_su_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">
          <div class="mixed_fraction gap_0">
            <span class="whole f32b">6&divide;</span>
            <span class="fraction_box f32b">
              <span>2</span>
              <span>3</span>
            </span>
          </div>
          를 어떻게 계산하는지 알아봅시다.
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="input_area">
          <article class="page page_1">
            <h3 lang="y">
              <img src="../../common_contents/common/img/title_heading_num_1.svg">
              의 그림을 이용하여 
              <div class="mixed_fraction gap_0">
                <span class="whole f32b">6&divide;</span>
                <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </span>
              </div>
              를 계산하는 방법을 알아보세요.
            </h3> 
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="mixed_fraction gap_0">
                <span class="whole f32b">6&divide;</span>
                <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </span>
              </div>
              <span class="f32b">=</span>
              <span class="f32b">(6&divide;</span>
              <span class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
              </span>
              <span class="f32b">)&times;</span>
              <span class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
              </span>
              <span class="f32b">=</span>
              <span class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="9"></math-field>
              </span>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_2">
            <h3 lang="y">
              자연수를 분수로 바꾸어
              <div class="mixed_fraction gap_0">
                <span class="whole f32b">6&divide;</span>
                <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </span>
              </div>
              를 계산하는 방법을 알아보세요.
            </h3> 
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="mixed_fraction gap_0">
                <span class="whole f32b">6&divide;</span>
                <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </span>
              </div>
              <span class="f32b">=</span>
              <span class="fraction_box">
                <span class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="24"></math-field>
                </span>
                <span class="f32b">3</span>
              </span>
              <span class="f32b">&divide;</span>
              <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                <span>2</span>
                <span>3</span>
              </span>
              <span class="f32b">=</span>
              <span class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
              </span>
              <span class="f32b">&divide;2=</span>
              <span class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
              </span>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_3">
            <h3 lang="y">(자연수)&divide;(분수)를 계산하는 방법을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                <ol class="example_box">
                  <li>자연수를 ‌ 분자로 나누고 분모를 곱합니다</li>
                  <li>자연수를 나누는 수와 분모가 같은 분수로 바꾼 다음 분자끼리 나누어 계산합니다.</li>
              </ol>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
